    "In those days the multitude being very great, and having nothing to eat, <span class=\"person\">Jesus</span> called his disciples unto him, and saith unto them,",
    "<span class=\"word\">I have compassion on the multitude, because they have now been with me three days, and have nothing to eat:</span>",
    "<span class=\"word\">And if I send them away fasting to their own houses, they will faint by the way: for divers of them came from far.</span>",
    "And his disciples answered him, From whence can a man satisfy these men with bread here in the wilderness?",
    "And he asked them, <span class=\"word\">How many loaves have ye?</span> And they said, Seven.",
