    "Saying, <span class=\"word\">Behold, we go up to <span class=\"place\">Jerusalem</span>; and the Son of man shall be delivered unto the chief priests, and unto the scribes; and they shall condemn him to death, and shall deliver him to the Gentiles:</span>",
